Package: stylehaven
Title: Quick style utilities and guides
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R: 
    person(given = "Camille",
           family = "Seaberry",
           role = c("aut", "cre"),
           email = "camille@ctdatahaven.org")
Description: This is a collection of style utilities mostly revolving around
  making clean labels for legible plots and (eventually) examples of building
  common plots. There's not a whole lot to it, probably never will be, just a
  collection of utilities, examples, and some best(?) practices.
